        <abstract> 
<p>Says he is forwarding the Smith, Elder &amp; Co. account to the Treasury. Discusses advertisements of <hi rend="italic">Zoology</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Coral reefs</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Volcanic islands</hi> "is almost ready for press".</p> 
